longBusinessSummary: VibroPower Corporation Limited, an investment holding company, designs, manufactures, supplies, installs, commissions, and services generators primarily for commercial and industrial, and housing projects in Singapore, Malaysia, China, Hong Kong, and internationally. It operates through three segments: Projects, Power Plant, and Others. The company also trades in, installs, commissions, and services diesel generators; and manufactures and repairs electric generators. In addition, it engages in the import, export, and sale of engines and spare parts; trade of generator parts and accessories; and development, operation, and management of power generation projects. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Singapore.
